ue, the Greek Cup and in the [[1993\u201394 UEFA Champions League|UEFA Champions League]].\n\n==Players==\n\n===Squad information===\n\n{{Fs start}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Spyros Ikonomopoulos]]|pos=GK}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Elias Atmatsidis]]|pos=GK}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Michalis Kasapis]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Vassilis Borbokis]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Vaios Karagiannis]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Stelios Manolas]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Giorgos Koutoulas]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Giorgos Agorogiannis]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Michalis Vlachos]]|pos=DF}}\n{{fs mid}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Charis Kopitsis]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=MKD|name=[[Toni Savevski]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Vassilios Tsiartas]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=Bosnia|name=[[Refik \u0160abanad\u017eovi\u0107]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Tasos Mitropoulos]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Alexis Alexandris]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Vasilis Dimitriadis]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=Bosnia|name=[[Zoran Sli\u0161kovi\u0107]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs end}}\n\n==Competitions==\n\n===Alpha Ethniki===\n====League table====\n{{:1993\u201394 Alpha Ethniki|showteam=AEK}}\n\n===Greek Cup===\n{{main|1993\u201394 Greek Football Cup}}\n====Final====\nThe 52nd [[Greek Football Cup|Greek Cup]] Final was played at the [[Olympic Stadium (Athens)|Athens Olympic Stadium \"Spyridon Louis\"]].\n\n{{football box|\ndate= April 20, 1994|\nteam1= Panathinaikos|\nscore= 3 &ndash; 3 <br> <small>([[Extra time|a.e.t.]])</small>|\nteam2= AEK Athens|\ngoals1= [[Krzysztof Warzycha|Warzycha]] {{goal|32}} <br> [[Stelios Manolas|Manolas]] {{goal|54|[[Own goal|o.g.]]}} <br> [[Dimitris Markos|Markos]] {{goal|116}} |\ngoals2= [[Alexandros Alexandris|Alexandris]] {{goal|72}} {{goal|95}} <br> [[Vasilis Dimitriadis|Dimitriadis]] {{goal|77}} 